cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

This paper is about active learning for natural language processing tasks, specifically sequence tagging. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also proposes a new method that adapts to the model being trained, which involves machine learning techniques, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. Additionally, the paper uses deep learning methods, which fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper proposes a new approach to reduce redundancy in active learning, which involves optimization techniques, making cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) another possible category.
